CryptoSubmit is a full automated timestamping framework, that makes use of OriginStamp. OriginStamp is a free trusted timestamping solution based on the Blockchain of Bitcoin.

CryptoSubmit tracks the legal origin of digital contant, such as [...]. These among are digital publications or event events and system interactions like user logins and comments.

[...], since most work is done by the OriginStamp-API.

Trusted timestamping keeps track of creation or modifying time of a digital document, thus prooving that a specific document has been existing in a specific form a certain  point in time to now.

